code: /**  * If true, an explicit `null bucket represents documents with missing values.  */ boolean missingBucket() {     return missingBucket. }

comment: /**  * The sort order for the values source (e.g. -1 for descending and 1 for ascending).  */
code: /**  * The sort order for the values source (e.g. -1 for descending and 1 for ascending).  */ int reverseMul() {     assert reverseMul == -1 || reverseMul == 1.     return reverseMul. }
